re, Wales, United Kingdom, his father, William Parriet, was 30 and his mother, Jane Hertford, was 25. He married Mable or Mary Caniston or Kynaston in 1272, in Prendergast, Pembrokeshire, Wales. They were the parents of at least 1 son. He lived in Prendergast, Pembrokeshire, Wales, United Kingdom in 1841. He died about 1338, in Wales, United Kingdom, at the age of 89."},"et":{"1250–about 1338":"1250–umbes 1338","1250–1338":"1250–1338","1252–Female":"1252–Surnud","1275–1338":"1275–1338","1220–Male":"1220–Surnud","1225–Female":"1225–Surnud","1338":"1338","1225":"1225","about 1338":"umbes 1338","1275":"1275","1220":"1220","1252":"1252","1250":"1250","1272":"1272","Wales, United Kingdom":"Wales, United Kingdom","Prendergast, Pembrokeshire, Wales":"Prendergast, Pembrokeshire, Wales","Heroldstone,Pembroke,Wales":"Pembrokeshire, Wales, United Kingdom","Heroldstone, Pembroke, Wales":"Pembrokeshire, Wales, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1250–about 1338":"1250–noin 1338","1250–1338":"1250–1338","1252–Female":"1252–Kuollut","1275–1338":"1275–1338","1220–Male":"1220–Kuollut","1225–Female":"1225–Kuollut","1338":"1338","1225":"1225","about 1338":"noin 1338","1275":"1275","1220":"1220","1252":"1252","1250":"1250","1272":"1272","Wales, United Kingdom":"Wales, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Prendergast, Pembrokeshire, Wales":"Prendergast, Pembrokeshire, Wales","Heroldstone,Pembroke,Wales":"Pembrokeshire, Wales, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Heroldstone, Pembroke, Wales":"Pembrokeshire, Wales, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1250–about 1338":"1250–environ 1338","1250–1338":"1250–1338","1252–Female":"1252–Décédée","1275–1338":"1275–1338","1220–Male":"1220–Décédé","1225–Female":"1225–Décédée","1338":"1338","1225":"1225","about 1338":"environ 1338","1275":"1275","1220":"1220","1252":"1252","1250":"1250","1272":"1272","Wales, United Kingdom":"Pays de Galles, Royaume-Uni","Prendergast, Pembrokeshire, Wales":"Prendergast, Pembrokeshire, Galles","Heroldstone,Pembroke,Wales":"Pembrokeshire, Pays de Gall